{ Always a move to check. It has been played by several 2600+ GMs so it certainly merits some attention. }
5... Na6
{ Forced. Despite being on the rim, the knight is certainly not dim. We're planning to kick back White's knight with ...c6 and can then reroute the knight to d6 with ... Nc7-e8-d6. }
6. e3 c6 7. Nc3 Nc7 8. Be2 { allows } 8... Bg4 9. O-O O-O
{ is very pleasant, when ...Nh5 as well as ...Ne6 + ...c5 are logical follow-ups. }
