10... a6
{ preparing ...Qc7 without allowing Nb5.   Note that  10...cxd4  does not win a pawn as White has the in-between move  11.Nxc6  Bxc6  12.exd4= }
11. O-O Qc7 { expells White's knight from e5 with a slight advantage. } *

