9. Qc2
{ 9.Qe2  is very similar.  9...e5  10.dxe5  Nxe5  11.Nxe5  Bxe5=  Black comfortably equalized and went on to win in 0-1 Abasov, N @@StartBracket@@2632@@EndBracket@@ - Dominguez, L @@StartBracket@@2763@@EndBracket@@ FIDE World Cup 2019. This game is analyzed in themodel games section.   9.e4?!  is premature on account of  9...cxd4  10.cxd4  dxe4  11.Nxe4  Nxe4  12.Bxe4  Nf6  13.Bd3  Qa5∓  when White loses castling rights. }
