{ may look clever for White. White's idea is that if we take on g3, we'll open the h-file for his rook. However, after... }
12... Bxg3 13. hxg3 h6
{ ...White has no way of making use of the h-file. Black has more space and superior control over the center so White should already start thinking about equalizing. }
