Nxe4 14. Bxe4 Nf6
{ Black has no problems.   For example  15.Qc2  Nxe4  16.Qxe4  Qb6  17.dxc5  Qxc5  18.Rac1  Qf5  19.Qxf5  Bxf5  20.Rc7  Be4=  covers the b7 pawn. Black is completely fine with ...Rad8 up next. }
