{ In the next 5 trainable lines, we discuss White's 5th move alternatives to 5. Bg3. These are mostly harmless, although Black should still know how best to react }
5. Ne5
{ is the most popular 5th move alternative with 1300+ OTB games.   5.Bxd6  has been played in 900+ OTB games.   5.Bd3  is less popular with 400+ OTB games.  Note that the no retreat lines with 5. Nbd2 are covered afterward. They are very subtle so it's best we check them once we've dealt with all these sidelines. }
