{ The alternative bishop development  10.Bf4  gets hit by  Nd5  11.Nxd5  cxd5  12.Bb3  c6∓  Black is simply a pawn up. }
10... Ng4 { hits the d4 pawn and prepares ...Qd6 to attack White's king. } 11.
Ne2 Qd6 12. Bf4 e5
{ Crashes through the center and breaks apart White's position. } *

