{ improves over the game 0-1 @@StartBracket@@42@@EndBracket@@ Kvakovszky,G @@StartBracket@@2025@@EndBracket@@-Kozelov,R @@StartBracket@@2149@@EndBracket@@ Saint Louis 2019. Black is threatening ...Qd5. }
