{ White will now have to spend valuable time getting the e-pawn back. } 7. Qe2
{ clears the way for queenside castling, which we can prevent with } 7... Qa5
8. c3
{ has never been played but is a natural move that deserves some attention. }
8... Nbd7 9. Nxe4 { 9.b4  only helps us activate our queen with  9...Qa3⩱ }
9... Nxe4 10. Qxe4 Qxc5 11. Nf3 Be7
