11... e4 { is a good illustration of why we went ...c6. After } 12. Ne1
{ we can simply bypass White's b-pawn with } 12... c5 13. Nc2 h6 14. Bf4 c4
{ gave Black a huge space advantage in the engine game Glaurung 2.0.1 - Deep Shredder 11, Internet 2008. Next up are ...Nb6 and ...Qe7. }
