9... Ng4 { The point is that } 10. f3 { runs into the stunning } 10... Nxe3 11.
Bxe3 cxd4
{ Black will recoup the sacrificed material with interest.   A sample continuation is  11...cxd4  12.Bxd4  Nxd4  13.h5  Be6  14.hxg6  hxg6−+  followed by ...Rfc8 with a big attack. The engines are already giving Black a decisive advantage. }
