9... Nc6
{ is an OTB novelty, improving over the game 1-0 @@StartBracket@@51@@EndBracket@@ Sharafiev,A @@StartBracket@@2435@@EndBracket@@-Yandemirov,V @@StartBracket@@2388@@EndBracket@@ Kazan 2016. Black is ready to push ahead with ...d4. }
