{ wins material.   A sample continuation is  13...Be6  14.Qxa5  Nxa5  15.Nxf6  Rxd1+  16.Kxd1  Nxc4  17.Ne4  Bd5  18.f3  Nxe3+  19.Kd2  Nxg2−+  Black is winning. }
