{ Black is in great shape and can look to break in the center with ...d4 next.   A sample continuation is  12...e5  13.g5  Nh5  14.Ng3  d4  15.Nxh5+?!  is natural but inaccurate.  15...gxh5  16.Ne4  Qb6  17.Qe1  Bf5⩱  when Black is already for choice. }
