14... Nxc5 15. Qxa2 Bxa2 16. Kd2
{ White is threatening to trap our bishop with b3, so we should drop it back with }
16... Bd5
{ with all to play for, ...f5 and ...Rfd8 being on the agenda. The position is objectively equal but I'd certainly pick Black here. }
