{ leaves White's king stranded in the middle of the board after   Also bad is  11.Bg5?!  h6  12.Bxf6  Qxf6  13.O-O  Bf5∓  Two bishops plus the center equal a clear Black advantage. }
11... Nxe5 12. Nxe5 Qe7 13. Nef3 Re8
{ White is in big trouble along the e-file. } *

