{ is White's most popular alternative to 6. c4 and has been essayed in over 3000 OTB games.   6.Nc3  occurred in 2100+ OTB games.   6.a4  has been played in 1900+ games   6.Re1  was seen in 1800+ OTB games.   6.Nbd2  is the 6th moves popular option with 1200+ OTB games.   6.c4  transposes to a mainline in the King's Indian, which is outside the scope of this course @@StartBracket@@as we're only dealing with d4 systems@@EndBracket@@. }
