10... dxe2 11. Qxe2 Bg4 { Moves the bishop to safety with tempo. } 12. Qb5 Qd7
13. Qxd7 Nbxd7
{ The engines assess this position as equal, but Black has every right to play for the full point. White's isolated d-pawn is a big target. }
