11... e3 12. f4 a5
{ Gains space on the queenside and prepares to develop the knight to ...a6. Black can also consider breaking with ...a4 in the future, creating counterplay along the a-file. A complex game lies ahead where Black has good prospects.   A sample continuation is  12...a5  13.Rac1  Na6  14.Na4  Rb8  15.Nc5  Nxc5  16.Bxc5  Bd7= }
